  <brief_title>Efficacy of Keppra in Acute Alcohol Related Seizure Control--A Pilot Study</brief_title>
  <official_title>A Pilot Study Examining the Efficacy of Keppra in Acute Alcohol Related Seizure Control in the Emergency Department Setting</official_title>
